		{"id":"2de4ed034583e6c2","type":"text","text":"# $[36,72]_2$","x":844,"y":4376,"width":130,"height":62,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"6c60845568104aef","type":"text","text":"# $[36,72]_2$","x":1064,"y":4376,"width":130,"height":62,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"327c40189efd6ddf","type":"text","text":"# $[36,72]_{32}$","x":1289,"y":4616,"width":130,"height":62,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"634002c58101722a","type":"text","text":"修了最初有 bug：context_to_channels.weight 和 gate.weight 都初始化为 0，导致 phase_context 支路死掉。后来改成：\n\nnn.init.xavier_uniform_(self.context_to_channels.weight)\n\nnn.init.zeros_(self.context_to_channels.bias)\n\nnn.init.xavier_uniform_(self.gate.weight, gain=0.1)\n\nself.gate.bias.fill_(_initial_logit(0.7))\n\nRaw checkpoint 里 phase 支路现在已非零：\n\nmemory_gate.context_to_channels.weight nonzero = 1024/1024\n\nresidual_gate.context_to_channels.weight nonzero = 1024/1024\n\n但指标提升很小，说明相位支路虽然活了，贡献不明显。主要性能提升仍来自 门控式记忆筛选 + MST 输出残差稳定，而不是 phase_context 本身。","x":29,"y":2120,"width":451,"height":560},
		{"id":"cafcf7e1ec201961","type":"text","text":"RMSE=0.8400","x":620,"y":2395,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"26a0512ad8c45740","type":"text","text":"PhaseGatedMST Raw\n RMSE 0.8411","x":129,"y":1920,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"6e553c2c1d7da387","type":"text","text":"ConvLSTM_MSTRefiner_Raw_seed11 RMSE: 0.9016","x":129,"y":1660,"width":250,"height":69,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"33d776fba813566e","type":"text","text":"LSTM去掉解码器，直接拿三个时间步最后一层的隐藏层接入MST，然后拿一个CNN预测头出结果，该方式是目前不加入SPHERE表现最好的，但是SPHERE对该模型无提升","x":480,"y":1618,"width":265,"height":182,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"ae701a779e645b02","type":"text","text":"把SimVP并联到ConvLSTM 非常成功","x":11,"y":1284,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"b26c2004c8b44fac","type":"text","text":"seed11 RMSE0.9278","x":335,"y":1285,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"3b8c42ca526bedb4","type":"text","text":"再加上SPHERE","x":17,"y":1461,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"5ea537f27865c118","type":"text","text":"seed11 RMSE 0.8854","x":335,"y":1461,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"5daad0928e61330f","type":"text","text":"分解成季节背景场和动力异常残差，Convlstm_CARefiner  RMSE0.9463","x":878,"y":1333,"width":322,"height":70},
		{"id":"54dca9c071def954","type":"text","text":"# BASELINE","x":-855,"y":1168,"width":250,"height":72,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"8be0d3a533d216c9","type":"text","text":"SimVP+SPHERE RMSE 0.9367(0.0148)","x":-585,"y":1037,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"346f11babde1ace2","type":"text","text":"TemporalTranslator中3D和2D并行，还是打不过RAW","x":134,"y":1048,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"5fe58d49feb213b0","type":"text","text":"SimVP_Hybrid3D RMSE0.9566","x":545,"y":1048,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"6266c7773639bff4","type":"text","text":"RMSE 0.9526(0.0131)","x":-865,"y":920,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"a3ad2318d76240f2","type":"text","text":"SimVP把TemporalTranslator替换成3D卷积核RMSE1.0784 还是稍逊于simvp","x":120,"y":827,"width":277,"height":93,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"5d17be6abb43cc32","type":"text","text":"SimVP_3DConv-RMSE1.0784","x":545,"y":844,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"c79ff37bd41bf655","type":"file","file":"论文/Gao_SimVP_Simpler_Yet_Better_Video_Prediction_CVPR_2022_paper.pdf","x":1000,"y":364,"width":302,"height":293},
		{"id":"0cba4ff4c12dc329","type":"text","text":"做了RNN-CNN-RNN变体和CNN-RNN-CNN-RNN-CNN变体，后者表现优于前者，略逊色于SimVP优于LSTM一族","x":120,"y":640,"width":320,"height":120,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"d3e15dc148694746","type":"text","text":"CRCRC-RMSE1.2279","x":545,"y":620,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"82de839d0cbcc037","type":"text","text":"RCR-RMSE1.3524","x":541,"y":731,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"ac831a565122c3eb","type":"text","text":"# [[SimVP]]","x":-335,"y":480,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"e70262e896416365","type":"file","file":"论文/maxent_icml.pdf","x":1400,"y":32,"width":360,"height":332},
		{"id":"bb7eeb7019c433b0","type":"text","text":"# [[Max-Ent]]","x":-335,"y":200,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"680ee80cdd0aeb9a","type":"text","text":"将臭氧经过条件最大熵，做出臭氧的条件适宜分布图后，再将条件适宜分布图送入Predrnnpp模型（无解码器，直接卷积）来预测火星臭氧，精度无提升","x":397,"y":32,"width":278,"height":150},
		{"id":"37bd7d1df9d2cdb9","type":"file","file":"论文/D-Linear.pdf","x":1880,"y":-160,"width":340,"height":318},
		{"id":"2e65846eb8fabd63","type":"text","text":"# [[D-Linear]]","x":-335,"y":-28,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"85678cd9bdbf0d03","type":"text","text":"将Dlinear后的两个线性分支替换成Predrnnpp模型（不带解码器，直接卷积出结果）来预测火星臭氧，精度提升及其有限","x":405,"y":-220,"width":262,"height":147},
		{"id":"c604cdcf385547f7","x":400,"y":2855,"width":250,"height":60,"type":"text","text":"RMSE 0.8328"}
	],
